ions its future growth, comparing it to larger cities on other planets such as Altair. While he acknowledges the potential benefits of having a partner from Earth, he is also aware of the element of chance involved in the wife draft system and the limited information they have about Earth women due to tall tales and rumors.&#10;&#10;Therefore, while Joe Hill has heard positive things about Earth women's sophistication and glamour, Karl's perspective is more focused on Landing City's growth and his own responsibilities, with a sense of uncertainty and apprehension about the wife draft process and what it will mean for him personally.">
